## Diagnostic

### Gets the current log level of the logger
POST  {{baseUrl}}/system/v1/diagnostics/reconfigureLogLevel?minLogLevel=Debug&maxLogLevel=Fatal&loggerName=Meshmakers.*

### Sets log level of Microsoft to debug
POST {{baseUrl}}/system/v1/diagnostics/reconfigureLogLevel?minLogLevel=Info&maxLogLevel=Fatal&loggerName=Microsoft.*

### Sets log level of Microsoft to warn
POST {{baseUrl}}/system/v1/diagnostics/reconfigureLogLevel?minLogLevel=Warn&maxLogLevel=Fatal&loggerName=Microsoft.*

### Sets log level of Microsoft to off
POST {{baseUrl}}/system/v1/diagnostics/reconfigureLogLevel?minLogLevel=Off&maxLogLevel=Off&loggerName=Microsoft.*




## MCP Tool Tests

### List Tools
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{tenantId}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 1,
  "method": "tools/list"
}


### Echo Tool - Basic Test
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{tenantId}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 2,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "Echo",
    "arguments": {
      "message": "Hello OctoMesh!"
    }
  }
}


### Get Available Types
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{tenantId}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 3,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "get_available_types",
    "arguments": {
      "includeAbstract": false
    }
  }
}

### Search Types
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{tenantId}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 4,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "search_types",
    "arguments": {
      "searchTerm": "Person",
      "includeAbstract": false
    }
  }
}

### Get Type Schema
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{tenantId}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 5,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "get_type_schema",
    "arguments": {
      "ckTypeId": "YourTypeId"
    }
  }
}

### Create Entity
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{tenantId}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 6,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "create_entity",
    "arguments": {
      "ckTypeId": "EnergyCommunity/Customer",
      "entityData": [
        {"attributePath": "Contact.FirstName", "value": "Gerald"},
        {"attributePath": "Contact.LastName", "value": "Lochner"},
        {"attributePath": "Contact.Email", "value": "xy@z.com"},
        {"attributePath": "Contact.Address.Street", "value": "test"},
        {"attributePath": "Contact.Address.Zipcode", "value": "5020"},
        {"attributePath": "Contact.Address.CityTown", "value": "test"},
        {"attributePath": "Contact.Address.NationalCode", "value": "AT"},
        {"attributePath": "TaxProcedureCreditNote", "value": 1}
      ]
    }
  }
}

### Query Entities Simple
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{tenantId}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 7,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "query_entities_simple",
    "arguments": {
      "ckTypeId": "YourTypeId",
      "simpleFilters": "{\"name\": \"Test Entity\"}",
      "limit": 10
    }
  }
}

### Query Entities (Advanced)
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{tenantId}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 8,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "query_entities",
    "arguments": {
      "ckTypeId": "YourTypeId",
      "filters": "{\"FirstName\": \"Gerald\", \"LastName\": \"Lochner\"}",
      "limit": 10,
      "offset": 0
    }
  }
}

### Get Entity By ID
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{tenantId}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 9,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "get_entity_by_id",
    "arguments": {
      "ckTypeId": "YourTypeId",
      "rtId": "YourRuntimeId"
    }
  }
}

### Update Entity
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{tenantId}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 10,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "update_entity",
    "arguments": {
      "ckTypeId": "YourTypeId",
      "rtId": "YourRuntimeId",
      "entityData": "{\"name\": \"Updated Entity\", \"value\": 456}"
    }
  }
}

### Navigate Associations
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{tenantId}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 11,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "navigate_associations",
    "arguments": {
      "ckTypeId": "YourTypeId",
      "rtId": "YourRuntimeId",
      "ckRoleId": "YourRoleId",
      "direction": "Outbound",
      "targetTypeId": "YourTargetTypeId"
    }
  }
}

